replyContent: Hey Krista, we would appreciate if you would review this app based on its own merits, and not on the availability of another. But so you're aware, Google has taken down several of our icon packs over an error regarding our privacy policy. We aim to have it worked out and to restore these apps soon. Hope you will give your review another thought.
